title: ONE DAY OR DAY ONE
itunes:title: ONE DAY OR DAY ONE
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
One Day... Or Day One. You decide! This is a powerful new motivational speech that will motivate you to take action TODAY, not tomorrow. One of the best motivational speechess featuring Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity), Dr. Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity) and Jim Merkel.


This video was created in collaboration with and made possible by the UAE Nation Brand Project.


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
